disclosure and restrictions on private employment for former Government employees
are in Office of Personnel Management and agency regulations implementing
Public Law 95-521, which amended <xref href="http://uscode.house.gov/browse.xhtml;jsessionid=114A3287C7B3359E597506A31FC855B3"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">18
U.S.C.207</xref>.</p>
